@startuml flujo-vpn
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam SequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam ParticipantFontSize 11

title Flujo VPN WireGuard — PC3 → R1-Linux → PC1

participant "PC3\n2001:db8:3::10\nwg0: fd00:2::2" as PC3 #FFF9C4
participant "R3" as R3 #C8E6C9
participant "R2" as R2 #C8E6C9
participant "R1-Linux\n2001:db8:12::1\nNAT66 DNAT :51820" as R1 #FFCC80
participant "PC1 WireGuard\nfd00:1::10\nwg0: fd00:2::1" as PC1 #F8BBD0

== Establecimiento del tunel ==

PC3 -> R3 : UDP dst=2001:db8:12::1:51820\n(WireGuard Handshake Init)
R3 -> R2 : forward (OSPFv3)
R2 -> R1 : UDP dst=2001:db8:12::1:51820

group ip6tables
  note over R1 #FFF3E0
    INPUT ACCEPT: UDP:51820
    DNAT: dst → fd00:1::10:51820
    MASQUERADE: src → fd00:1::1
  end note
end

R1 -> PC1 : UDP dst=fd00:1::10:51820\nHandshake Init
PC1 --> R1 : Handshake Response
R1 --> PC3 : Handshake Response\nsrc=2001:db8:12::1

note over PC3 #E8F5E9
  Tunel establecido
  PC3 obtiene fd00:2::2/64
  AllowedIPs: fd00:1::/64, fd00:2::/64
end note

== Trafico sobre el tunel ==

PC3 -> R1 : UDP cifrado WireGuard\n(trafico a fd00:1::10)
R1 -> PC1 : trafico descifrado\ndst=fd00:1::10

note over PC3,PC1 #E3F2FD
  PC3 accede a intranet.dominio.local
  DNS dominio.local resuelve a fd00:1::10
  HTTP nginx sirve pagina privada
end note

@enduml
